00:04:29.270 --> 00:04:32.060
V-V-V...

00:04:32.270 --> 00:04:34.980
Vegeta!

00:05:55.180 --> 00:05:57.980
Kahretsin!

00:05:59.230 --> 00:06:00.560
Hey!

00:06:00.770 --> 00:06:03.570
